DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T100000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260321T120000
SUMMARY:Spring Symposium:  Radiant Health
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**Event Description**\nJoin us in exploring the connection between consciousness\, spiritual awareness\, and radiant health. We will discover how meditation\, emotional coherence\, breath\, and inner awareness can influence well-being at the cellular\, psychological\, and spiritual levels. From the relationship between consciousness and DNA\, to the sacred power of the breath\, the physiology of joy\, and the Rosicrucian practice of distance healing\, each session blends science\, mystical wisdom\, and practical techniques. During the program we will learn to cultivate harmony within oneself while extending healing and lovingkindness throughout the world.\n\nHere is the schedule:\n**10:00 am PDT**\n**DNA and Radiant Health with Grand Master Julie Scott**\nIn this experiential presentation\, we will explore the powerful connection between consciousness\, emotion\, and our molecular blueprint - DNA. Blending science with personal insight\, we will examine how meditation\, brain waves\, and emotional coherence may influence gene expression and cellular health. We will also learn how DNA functions as the body’s biochemical instruction system and how inner states can affect overall well-being. The session culminates in a guided meditation designed to cultivate love and coherence while consciously attuning to the vibratory intelligence within every cell.\n\n**10:30 am PDT**\n**The Breath of Life – Elemental Healing with Deborah Nelson**\nFrom the beginning of time\, humanity has reflected on the mystery of life. Sacred wisdom tells us that Divinity formed humanity from the dust of the earth and breathed into our nostrils the breath of life\, and humans became living beings. This presentation explores the sacred nature of the Breath of Life\, the intermediary through which the Universal Soul interacts with the body. Beyond oxygen\, each breath carries a cosmic essence\, an organizing intelligence across cultures known as Ka\, Prana\, Qi\, or Ruach. Whether we are aware of it or not\, imbalance within our psychic body gives rise to diseases. Through conscious awareness of our divine breath\, we quiet mental clutter\, deepen inner stillness\, and reconnect with our spiritual origin. The Breath of Life is a pathway to radiant health - revitalizing our cells and restoring harmony to mind and body.\n\n**11:00 am PDT**\n**Wellness and Wellbeing: The Physiology of Joy and Inner Awareness with RoseMarie Toussaint\, MD**\nIn this presentation\, we will explore the physiology of joy and the body’s remarkable capacity to experience inner harmony. Drawing from neuroscience and contemplative traditions\, we will examine how the brain’s “joy chemistry”—including serotonin\, dopamine\, and oxytocin—supports emotional balance\, resilience\, and connection. Through interoception and introspection\, the natural faculties that allow us to perceive and reflect upon signals arising within the body\, participants will discover how inner awareness reveals subtle rhythms and vibratory movements of life energy traditionally described as prana. The gentle vibrations produced by sacred vowel sounds can also be perceived internally\, inviting deeper sensitivity to these subtle currents of vitality. Through attentive awareness of these inner movements\, qualities such as calm\, compassion\, clarity\, and inner balance naturally emerge. The presentation concludes with a brief experiential practice cultivating coherence as well as radiant wellness and well-being.\n\n**11:30 am PDT**\n**Giving Spiritual Aid: The Rosicrucian Art of Distance Healing with Ingrid Young**\nWe live in a vibratory universe\, and Rosicrucian students are invited to learn a specific method whereby they can serve humanity anonymously through distance healing. During the 1930s\, Harvey Spencer Lewis introduced a special technique that he called "Absent Healing." In this short presentation\, you will learn not only the technique but also have access to important reminders and best practices as well as discover broader applications for its use. This presentation includes a meditation that invites you to participate at a high level of Cosmic attunement as we project radiant health to all living beings.\n\n**Please RSVP to access log-in link. Click Attend Online button below.**
