SUMMARY:Pronaos Convocation and Officer Installation
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n**Pronaos Convocation for Rosicrucian Members Only**\n**Installation of Officers**\n\n**Pronaos Topic - Education**\n**Presented by Frank Nappi\, F.R.C.**\nAll current members of the Rosicrucian Order AMORC are cordially invited to participate in this first convocation of the Rosicrucian New Year. We will be installing new officers and celebrating the return of the Spring season and the start of Rosicrucian year 3379.\n\n• Important to know- Doors open for members of the Rosicrucian Order by 6:30 PM. Please arrive early! Members - please bring your credentials or membership dues receipt.\n\nFollowing the meeting:\n1st Tuesday- Mystical Seekers Series Public Presentation at 8:00 PM\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos operates under the law of AMRA. You may give as your heart and mind direct you.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos is a 501c3 educational non-profit\, an affiliated body of the Rosicrucian English Grand Lodge for the Americas and the Caribbean.
