SUMMARY:First Tuesday Mystical Seekers Series
DESCRIPTION:Rosicrucians AMORC\, Santa Rosa\, CA\n-Free Admission - Refreshments - Open to the public -\n\nTopic to be announced.....\nSpeaker to be announced......\n\nAbout the Santa Rosa Pronaos\nWe hold a monthly public presentation on mystical or metaphysical topics as a public service. The topics and speakers vary and no previous knowledge or experience is required. Just bring an open mind and heart.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos doesn't charge for admission. We operate under the law of AMRA. You may give as your heart and mind direct you.\n\nThe Santa Rosa Pronaos of the Rosicrucian Order\, AMORC is a 501c3 Educational Nonprofit.
